---
import Menu from "../components/Menu.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Data Center College of the Philippines - Baguio City">
	<main class="container">
		<Menu />

		<div class="landing-page">
			<h1>Data Center College of the Philippines - Baguio City</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="introduction-section">
			PIONEERING IN IT EDUCATION SINCE 1974 Data Center College of the
			Philippines Baguio City - a haven for knowledge-seekers nestled in
			the chilly mountains of Baguio City! At DCCP Baguio, you'll find
			state-of-the-art facilities that cater to a variety of courses and
			programs, from information technology and business administration to
			hospitality and tourism management. With modern classrooms,
			laboratories, and simulation rooms, you'll have all the tools you
			need to hone your skills and develop your expertise in your chosen
			field. What sets DCCP Baguio apart from other colleges is its
			commitment to experiential learning. Here, you won't just be sitting
			in lectures and taking exams - you'll be actively engaging in
			real-world scenarios and industry partnerships that will prepare you
			for the challenges of the workforce. But it's not just about
			academics and career preparation at DCCP Baguio - there's also a
			strong emphasis on personal growth and community service. Through
			various student organizations and outreach programs, you'll have the
			opportunity to develop your leadership skills and give back to the
			community. So if you're ready to embark on a journey of learning,
			growth, and endless possibilities, come join the DCCP Baguio family
			today!
		</div>

		<div class="scholarships-section">
			<h1>Images Here</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="courses-offered-section">
			<h1>Coursr</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="contact-section"></div>

		<Footer />
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
	}

	.landing-page {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		height: 100vh;
		width: 100%;
		background-image: url("/images/landing-page-background.jpg");
		background-size: cover;
		background-repeat: no-repeat;
		background-blend-mode: darken;
		background-color: #070720;
	}

	h1 {
		color: #1c1d22;
		font-size: 4rem;
	}
</style>
